{"rule_id":"kakari_ya_ka_rentai","category":"kakari_musubi","trigger":"や|か","expected_form":"連体形","allowed_endings":["く","き","む","る","たる","ける","なる","ぬる","ざる","べき","らむ","める"],"bad_patterns":["や.*なり。","か.*なり。"],"positive_examples":["いかでか知らむ。","誰や来る。"],"negative_examples":["いかでか知りけり。"],"weight":4}
